00:39:50,930 --> 00:39:53,182
and then begging me to come back.

633
00:39:53,265 --> 00:39:56,143
Cooper has never hurt me.

634
00:39:57,770 --> 00:39:58,813
[scoffs]

635
00:39:58,896 --> 00:40:01,440
He deserves so much better than this.

636
00:40:02,066 --> 00:40:04,652
